<hl>
<seg id=1> City construction became the new popular investment in Qinghai. </seg>
</hl>
<p>
<seg id=2> Xinhua News Agency, Xiling, 21 December Basic city construction drew the attention of foreign businessmen and became the new popular investment in Qinghai. </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=3> There had been a Lack of investment in construction in Xiling City for a long time. The total investment from 1949 to 1995 was only about 400 million Yuan, which restricted economic development. </seg>
<seg id=4> In the last two years, some foreign businessmen showed their interest in the construction of Xiling City. </seg>
<seg id=5> The Qinghai government made the best use of the situation and put forward the idea of making basic construction commercial, and they approved Certain Regulations to Encourage the Foreign Investment at the beginning of this year. </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=6> After the right of road building in the east of Xiling was transferred, there were more than 10 foreign businessmen holding talks on the business, and the final price was 50 million Yuan. </seg>
<seg id=7> A Hong Kong businessman undertook the construction project at Mojia Street, and the investment was 50 million Yuan. </seg>
<seg id=8> The sixth water-improvement project used 40 million Yuan in foreign capital, and the water supply could be 150,000 tons per day, which solved the city's water problem. </seg>
<seg id=9> The contract for the road-building project in the north of the city had been signed by Hong Kong Taihua Company, and the investment was 180 million Yuan. The talks on the highway project along the south city were carrying on. </seg>
</p>
